# Mosquitto ACL — least privilege, even in the POC.
#
# hass : the Home Assistant backend. Needs full read/write (it subscribes to
#        discovery + all device topics, and may publish commands).
# iot  : sensor devices / the simulator. May ONLY publish their telemetry and
#        their Home Assistant discovery configs. No read, no other topics.

user hass
topic readwrite #

user iot
topic write home/#
topic write homeassistant/#
